On the bottom, before Service Info: yada yada, we see _http-title: Login.
Which tells us that we have a login page and as we copy paste the machine's Ip address into the url/address bar WE DO indeed get prompted with a login page!

Afterwards, lets right click and view page source! Or, well... CTRL + U as told by the plaintext...

We notice on the bottom, where the green text is located, that the source code contains guest credentials.






